ta-text=\"αὐτῷ\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"αὐτός\">ΑΥΤΩ</span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"κῖτε\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">ΚΙΤΕ</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Αὐξάνων\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Αὐξάνων\"><span data-text=\"Αὐξάνων\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"Αὐξάνων\">ΑΥΞΑΝΩΝ</span></span></span><br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-text=\"ὁ\" data-n=\"65\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">Ο</span><span data-text=\"τούτου\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"οὗτος\">ΤΟΥΤΟΥ</span><span data-text=\"υἱὸς\" data-n=\"75\" data-lemma=\"υἱός\">ΥΙΟΣ</span><br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span><span data-text=\"βιώσας\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"βιόω\">ΒΙΩΣΑΣ</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"85\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span><span data-text=\"κε\" data-n=\"90\" data-lemma=\"κε\">ΚΕ</span><br id=\"al7-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>⸙</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\">l.2 reg., orig. ΤΟΙΜΒΟΣτοίμβος</p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"τύμβος\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"τύμβος\">ΤΥΜΒΟΣ</span><span data-text=\"Σαβίνου\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"Σάβινος\">ΣΑΒΙΝΟΥ</span><span data-text=\"ἐν\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ἐν\">ΕΝ</span><span data-text=\"αὐτῷ\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"αὐτός\">ΑΥΤΩ</span><span data-text=\"κῖτε\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">ΚΙΤΕ</span><span data-text=\"Αὐξάνων\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"Αὐξάνων\">ΑΥΞΑΝΩΝ</span><span data-text=\"ὁ\" data-n=\"65\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">Ο</span><span data-text=\"τούτου\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"οὗτος\">ΤΟΥΤΟΥ</span><span data-text=\"υἱὸς\" data-n=\"75\" data-lemma=\"υἱός\">ΥΙΟΣ</span><span data-text=\"βιώσας\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"βιόω\">ΒΙΩΣΑΣ</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"85\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span><span data-text=\"κε\" data-n=\"90\" data-lemma=\"κε\">ΚΕ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>text as per Crispi, Kaibel in IG, Orsi (Kaibel omits the second hedera in line 1)</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>Tomb of Sabinos, in this lies Auxanon, son of this man, having lived 25 years</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>One of several inscriptions described by Crispi as coming from Taormina but commonly attributed to Siracusa.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Crispi 1823 264 no.5 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002230\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002230</a>  </li><li> Kirchhoff 1877 9466 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001249\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001249</a>  </li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">166</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a>  </li><li> Strazzulla 1897 no. 107 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001390\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001390</a>  </li><li> Rizzo 1904 116 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10003144\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10003144</a>  </li><li> Wessel 1989 49 no.188 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394</a>  </li><li> Muscolino 2011-2012 234 G22 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002215\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002215</a>  </li><li> Orsi 2018 Tacc. 2, p.9 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002617\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002617</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li> Ferrua 1989 no. 481 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995</a>  </li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1-5  17  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
